        {
            "title": "旺角黃衫男疑被的士撞 與的哥上演街頭MMA 雙雙被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"的士司機與黃衣男街頭爆MMA ，雙雙被捕。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5c3fee38cf6b10fc2b95faae7debbcfb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250414/_2025041400224992335.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">的士司機與黃衣男街頭爆MMA ，雙雙被捕。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>社交平台周日（13日）流傳三段影片，片中見到兩名中年男子在旺角街頭上演一場長達10分鐘的MMA，期間二人連環爆粗，拳來腳往，扭作一團，有途人上前勸阻，同時引來多名途人駐足圍觀。\n\n</p>\n<p>第一段影片見到一輛的士當時停在山東街及通菜街交界，車旁有兩名中年男子互毆，其中一名相信是的士司機的黑衣男子向黃衣男使出右勾拳，黃衣男亦不甘示弱，將黑衣男推向路邊欄杆。當時有一名外籍青年上前勸交拉住黃衣男，的士司機反問黃衣男「你做咩打我塊鏡呀？」，同時又拾起遺留在路邊的一對鞋；黃衫男趁機向的士司機還擊，雙方再次倒在地上扭作一團。\n\n</p>\n<p>外籍青年隨後將兩人分開，黃衣男立即着圍觀的途人協助報警，並稱：「我都唔知咩事？我X你老X，佢撞到我。」的士司機亦將車駛至路邊的士站。雙方隨後再爆口角，黃衣男稱：「打我囉，你咁惡」，的士司機則指對方：「你惡先㗎，你打我塊鏡」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193504/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士司機倒在地上。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35a07a318c0bde7d1077dea71add112b/2025-04/2025-04-14_00_01_19.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士司機倒在地上。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193505/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩人扭作一團。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef8ca064c6553fb8db750c1198c01df5/2025-04/2025-04-14_00_02_21.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩人扭作一團。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193506/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"雙方在街頭互毆。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/00125e0b82ccb5ef35b19c23bcfa9a0b/2025-04/2025-04-13_23_47_53.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雙方在街頭互毆。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193507/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"外籍青年圖將兩人分開。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ba76921b9409707a58c71a4a800ca46/2025-04/2025-04-13_23_48_00.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        外籍青年圖將兩人分開。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193508/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"外籍青年圖將兩人分開。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10b1e9e85c89b45d2404f29dbaa0f80e/2025-04/2025-04-13_23_48_07.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        外籍青年圖將兩人分開。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193509/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃衣男稱被的士撞到。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da5f232f9425d31d4f2d91939ca28dfb/2025-04/2025-04-13_23_53_15.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃衣男稱被的士撞到。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193510/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士司機則指黃衣男打爛的士側鏡。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4d427684ca70bcb403ba5cb157be6bc/2025-04/2025-04-13_23_55_37.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士司機則指黃衣男打爛的士側鏡。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>在第二段影片，黃衣男以粗口罵對方，並多次出手推開的士司機。兩人再於馬路上發生打鬥，的士司機倒在地上，黃衣衫連續多次起腳踢向對方，的士司機立即企起揮拳還擊。雙方隨後再發生多次拉扯及推撞後，片段亦隨之結束。\n\n</p>\n<p>事發於周日晚上10時許，一輛的士駛至旺角山東街及通菜街交界時撞到一名男途人，警方接報到場，見到男司機與一名男子發生口角，繼而動武。經初步調查後，兩名男子涉嫌「在公眾地方打鬥」被捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息指，黃衣男當時正在過馬路，見到的士駛至時未有退後，反而繼續向前行，黑衫司機不停響鞍，黃衣男不滿的士沒有讓路，竟揮拳毀壞的士倒後鏡，雙方最終發生衝突，拳來腳往。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063764/即時-港聞-旺角黃衫男疑被的士撞-與的哥上演街頭MMA-雙雙被捕",
